title: Selections from The Typewriter and Tory
description:
This is the EP from composer Matthew Bouchard which has highlights from both musicals, The Typewriter and Tory. Please review the EP, and spread the word. Plans for the Concept album of The Typewriter is in motion, and Tory will be playing at a theater local to the composer. The songs are played on solo piano by the composer and recorded using Audacity 1.3 Beta.

From the composer: Many thanks to everyone for helping with this small, yet significant project. Both shows are really moving forward, especially The Typewriter. Many thanks to my "family" in Costa Rica who were so inspiring to this project.
